body:
Wolves-Esports is excited to announce open recruitment for League of Legends!

We are currently looking to recruit a new team to add to our Pro team roster based in Europe. We would prefer a pre-existing team with some achievements under their belt. Ideally, all players should be at least Diamond ELO. While this isn&#039;t a hardline requirement, it definitely helps.

Team members will be expected to represent us in a professional manner at all times, and be able to fulfill a set of requirements that include (but are not limited to): regularly scheduled practices, consistent activity in online competitions, a desire to create and grow this team into something more, and other more specific requirements.


What are the requirements:

- 18+;
- Europe;
- Fluent English;
- Mature behavior;
- Serious approach to practice and to play official games;
- Focus on League of Legends as the only competitive game;
- Regularly scheduled practices;
- Consistent activity in online competitions;

If you are able to schedule streaming sessions, it would be a major advantage for your application.


What can you expect:

- Voice Server;
- A professional and experienced management;
- Fast developing and growing organization;
- To have all kinds of support available for Wolves-Esports;


What other games do we Support?

League of Legends
Counter Strike: Global Offensive
Heroes of the Storm
World of Tanks
Hearthstone
Dota 2
Smite


If you are interested, please visit our website: www.wolves-esports.com, and email us at: robert@wolves-esports.com with more information about what you bring.



Best regards,

Robert &quot;muuuhli&quot; M.

Team Manager for Wolves-Esports

